MATCH (p)-[:HAS_CONTENT]->(content)
MATCH (p)-[:HAS_LOCATION]->(location)
MATCH (p)-[:HAS_LANGUAGE]->(language)
MATCH (p)-[:CREATED_AT]->(created_at)

请将以下自然语言翻译为对该数据库的Cypher查询:
查找名为Wojciech的人及其认识的人的相关信息，包括他们的浏览器使用情况、生日、性别、创建日期、电子邮件、语言、位置IP以及关系的创建日期，限制返回10条结果。返回的信息包括：Wojciech的浏览器使用情况、生日、性别、创建日期、电子邮件、语言、位置IP、ID；他认识的人的浏览器使用情况、生日、性别、创建日期、位置IP、姓名、姓氏、ID。
output:
MATCH (p:Person {name: 'Wojciech'})-[:KNOWS]->(k:Person)
OPTIONAL MATCH (p)-[browser:USES]->(browserUsage)
WITH p, k, browserUsage
MATCH (k)-[:USES]->(kBrowserUsage)
WITH p, k, browserUsage, kBrowserUsage
MATCH (p)-[email:EMAIL]->(emailInfo)
WITH p, k, browserUsage, kBrowserUsage, emailInfo
MATCH (p)-[language:LANGUAGE]->(languageInfo)
WITH p, k, browserUsage, kBrowserUsage, emailInfo, languageInfo
MATCH (p)-[location:LOCATION]->(locationInfo)
WITH p, k, browserUsage, kBrowserUsage, emailInfo, languageInfo, locationInfo
MATCH (k)-[created_at:CREATED_AT]->(kCreatedAt)
WITH p, k, browserUsage, kBrowserUsage, emailInfo, languageInfo, locationInfo, kCreatedAt
MATCH (browserUsage)-[browserDetails:DETAILS]->(browserDetailsInfo)
WITH p, k, browserUsage, kBrowserUsage, emailInfo, languageInfo, locationInfo, kCreatedAt, browserDetailsInfo
RETURN p.name AS Name, p.birthday AS Birthday, p.gender AS Gender, p.created_at AS CreatedAt, p.email AS Email, p.language AS Language, p.locationIP AS LocationIP, id(p) AS ID,
       k.name AS KnowsName, k.surname AS KnowsSurname, k.birthday AS KnowsBirthday, k.gender AS KnowsGender, k.created_at AS KnowsCreatedAt, k.locationIP AS KnowsLocationIP, id(k) AS KnowsID,
       CASE WHEN browserUsage IS NOT NULL THEN browserUsage.name ELSE 'Unknown' END AS WojciechBrowserUsage,
       CASE WHEN kBrowserUsage IS NOT NULL THEN kBrowserUsage.name ELSE 'Unknown' END AS KnowsBrowserUsage,
       CASE WHEN emailInfo IS NOT NULL THEN emailInfo.address ELSE 'Unknown' END AS WojciechEmail,
       CASE WHEN languageInfo IS NOT NULL THEN languageInfo.code ELSE 'Unknown' END AS WojciechLanguage,
       CASE WHEN locationInfo IS NOT NULL THEN locationInfo.ip ELSE 'Unknown' END AS WojciechLocationIP,
       CASE WHEN browserDetailsInfo IS NOT NULL THEN browserDetailsInfo.details ELSE 'Unknown' END AS WojciechBrowserDetails,
       CASE WHEN kCreatedAt IS NOT NULL THEN kCreatedAt.date ELSE 'Unknown' END AS KnowsCreatedAt
LIMIT 10
